  "prompt": "What does \"RIC\" mean with reference to email?",
  "response": "In the context of email, \"RIC\" typically stands for \"Read Immediately or Comment.\" It is often used as an instruction or reminder in professional settings, indicating that the recipient should read the email promptly and may need to provide feedback or comments. However, it's worth noting that acronyms can have different meanings depending on the specific context or industry, so it's always good to confirm with the specific sender if you're uncertain.",
